Apple Macintosh OS X Build Configuration
[Build Configuration]

Collaboration diagram for Apple Macintosh OS X Build Configuration:

Detailed Description

These macros are available to alter the functionality of the toolkit built for Apple Macintosh OS X platforms.


Defines

#define EXPAT_CONFIG_MACOSX
 This macro must be defined when building on OS X platforms as it configures the expat.h headers definition of XMLCALL correctly.
